title: #351: Tataria, The Titanic, Direct Energy Weapons and Melted Buildings With Redbricks and Annabelle
description:
Thank you so much for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we go deep with independent researchers Redbrick and Annabelle and their theories about Tataria, the clues left around the world and what they believed happened to very advanced civilization. This one goes really deep so enjoy and thank you for your support.
